  "texts": [
    "Despite the ML advantages, in the current context of multiple organizations, anomalies have occurred that could result in money laundering, identity theft and credit card fraud in the financial domain, medical errors and a decreased patient survival rate in the clinical domain, as well as a decline in student enrolment and a higher teacher attrition rate in the educational domain.",
    "This paper uses explainable AI technologies to approach the particular problem of predicting and detecting anomalies using a certain technology, namely an ML-based model, using a dataset of customers' financial transactions.",
    "We developed an automated process for performing this task in future transactions and improving the decision-making processes.",
    "We, therefore, studied recent literature that presents a wide range of highlighted datasets, AI technologies used to detect anomalies, and the relevant supplemental material.",
    "ML uses data and algorithms to gradually imitate how humans interact to improve AI programs' accuracy (Chen et al., 2021; Jarrin et al., 2019; Sarker et al., 2021)."
  ],
